{"id":"f3e56515-d148-416b-b73d-76e354b12764","name":"Lucio | YOUR MAIN VILLAIN","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 180, 255)\"><strong>[Villain!Bot x Hero!User] [You both have been faking to hate each other for a while. In a mission gone wrong, you take the blow that would've knocked him out.] [ANYPOV]</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 180, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">The villain you choose to save. 💜</mark></strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 0, 129)\">. ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 57, 135)\">. ݁. ݁₊ ⊹ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(110, 97, 171)\">. ݁˖ . ݁. ݁₊</span><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 143, 206)\"> ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(170, 177, 229)\"> ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁</span></p><hr><p><em>You're a pillar of hope and success. A true hero that emerged from the wicked and hated, from the whispered and mocked. You had powers and you used it for good, for the benefit of society. You played your role until the cameras were off. But when you were finally free from the prying eyes? You'd have your villain in your arms.</em></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 0, 129)\">. ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 57, 135)\">. ݁. ݁₊ ⊹ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(110, 97, 171)\">. ݁˖ . ݁. ݁₊</span><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 143, 206)\"> ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(170, 177, 229)\"> ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 2, 66)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">|</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 4, 239)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">|</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 209, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">|</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(9, 0, 55)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(225, 221, 255); color: inherit\">Author's note:</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 196, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"> So it's pretty established here that you two fight each other in field and love each other behind the curtains. You're free to choose your own power but be mindful that in the Initial Message you're gravely injured (you can make up your own excuse for it, maybe your power doesn't help, maybe you panic, maybe you survive or you die). You can play around a lot.</mark></strong></span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 2, 66)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">|</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 4, 239)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">|</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 209, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">|</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(13, 0, 70)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(228, 222, 255); color: inherit\">The man behind the mask is softer than he looks. But only for you.</mark></strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a4bce55e-779e-4aac-b1eb-be0493e69bd4_97ffa52c-cfd6-4e05-9f1c-96ca4b3fdcaa.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/uc8n32.webp\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">[Click]</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"a4bce55e-779e-4aac-b1eb-be0493e69bd4_15d0f708-17b8-479f-a74f-9f7c3f64b523.webp","creator":"L-y-r-a","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst